Primary Outcome Measures:
Monitor the levels of MSRV-Env expression in MS patients (according to McDonald criteria) of different diagnostic subgroups (RRMS, SPMS, PPMS, CIS), Monitor the levels of MSRV-Env expression in MS patients (according to McDonald criteria) of different diagnostic subgroups (RRMS, SPMS, PPMS, CIS) over time using 3 approaches:

* MSRV transcripts in PBMC;
* MSRV transcripts in plasma;
* MSRV-Env protein in serum., 1 year
